Act as a Twitter <-> IRC gateway/client for a single Twitter account per
instance of script.

The files you need to run this on your bot are:
- oauth.tcl
- twitter.tcl

You can download the script by clicking Download Source near the top of this page. Or you can get just the above 2 files by going to their page on here and downloading the "raw" version in the upper right corner of the source view.

Please read their header comments for usage information!
